00:03:50.630 --> 00:03:55.670
It's, I think, much easier at
drawing the user into the most

00:03:55.670 --> 00:03:56.660
important metrics.

00:03:56.660 --> 00:03:59.270
You can also
configure the page now

00:03:59.270 --> 00:04:02.240
